item.title: CVE-2023-48418|2024-08-02T21:30:35.154Z -- google -- pixel%20watch
item.description: In checkDebuggingDisallowed of DeviceVersionFragment.java, there is a possible way to access adb before SUW completion due to an insecure default value. This could lead to local escalation of privilege with no additional execution privileges needed. User interaction is not needed for exploitation

item.title: CVE-2023-4164|2024-08-02T07:17:12.260Z -- google -- pixel%20watch
item.description: There is a possible information disclosure due to a missing permission check. This could lead to local information disclosure of health data with no additional execution privileges needed.
